review_text: This might be one of the lesser of the teen sex comedies that came out of the success of the American Pie franchise and according to my previous rating I apparently didn't care for it, but with the Unrated version finally getting a Blu-ray release (previously only available on DVD), I had a good time with this one. It's not great and some things didn't work, I did like the core cast and some fun cameos. **3.25/5**
Excusy excusy! This movie is so hilarious. Kind of a raunchy comedy. Stays pretty funny throughout film.
